  "title": "Network Engineer, Technical Services (A004)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Industry: </strong>Broadband, Telecommunications Industry</p><p><strong>Location: </strong>Central area</p><p><strong>Skills:</strong> Network, Network Security Products</p><p><br /></p><p>This position will focus on enterprise network security support and services for various commercial clients island-wide.</p><p><br /></p><p>As the Senior Engineer, will also be serve as the technical lead to the team who will also provide guidance and technical expertise support.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Position Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Will be the Senior and subject matter expert in SDWAN, SDLAN, switches, cloud virtual firewalls.</li><li>Handle project roll-out, execution, implementation and delivery of related technology projects.</li><li>Serve as technical specialist (L2/L3) and subject matter expert to the team.</li><li>Responsible for documentation, reports for faults and resolutions, change request for clients.</li></ul><p><strong>Position Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Computer Engineering or related field.</li><li>4 to 6 years working experience in Network, IT Security Maintenance in a IT or Telecommunications environment.</li><li>Product knowledge with Cisco, SDWAN, SDLAN, Fortinet, Ruckus, ZTNA with experience working on various network equipment (eg: Router, Switches, Firewall).</li><li>Network certifications such as CCNA, CCNP, NSE 4, PCNSE a strong advantage.</li><li>PMP, Prince2 Certification is a strong advantage.</li></ul><p>We will consider all candidates but will prioritise those who have closer requirements to client needs.</p><p><br /></p><p>Thank you!</p><p><br /></p><p>Joseph Syho</p><p>Reg Number: R1108657</p><p>EA Licence No: 18C9079</p>",
